[Name] Gengetopt
[Summary] Gengetopt is a tool to write command line option parsing code for C programs.
[Description]
Gengetopt is a tool to generate C code to parse the command line arguments argc and argv that are part of every C or C++ program.
The generated code uses the C library function getopt_long to perform the actual command line parsing.
[License] GPLv3
[Homepage] https://www.gnu.org/software/gengetopt/
